<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الإِجَاج]</span>: لغة في الوِجاح <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
